    <div class="infobox">
        <h2 class="infobox-header">The Story</h2>
        <p class="infobox-text">
            What do seven sneaker freaks do when there's no golden place to get the best sneakers?
            Create their own golden place of course!
        </p>
    </div>

    <div class="infobox" id="parallax"></div>

