            To serve the best, we need to be the best.
            We aim high, shoot straight and deliver top-notch shoes for top-notch people!
        </p>
    </div>

    <div class="infobox" id="parallax"></div>

    <div class="infobox">
        <h2 class="infobox-header">The Promise</h2>
        <p class="infobox-text">
